videos.description:
A journey through the Burke Mountain area of Vermont's Northeast Kingdom,  Rasputitsa has become a staple of Vermont's gravel season. In this video, Phil tackles the epic 100k route, making friends with bolt cutters and hot dog vendors ("nothing says hydration like a hot dog"), drinking everything anyone gives him and finding legs he didn't know he had at this point in the season.

With respect and in memory of Richard “Rick” J. Wanstall
July 8, 1968 - April 29, 2023

